  {
    "title": "GitLab推出命令行工具，将整个开发流程带到了终端上",
    "url": "https://www.infoq.cn/article/ujS6Zt0ujfm4vUDe6shu",
    "summary": "<p>DevOps工具供应商<a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">GitLab</a>\"宣布推出<a href=\"https://github.com/profclems/glab?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">glab</a>\"——一个用于与GitLab交互的<a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/whatis/whatis_cli.asp?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">命令行工具</a>\"，进一步将触角延伸到<a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/direction/create/editor_extension/#where-we-are-headed?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">代码编写过程的所有阶段</a>\"。</p><p></p><p>glab是用<a href=\"https://go.dev/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">Go</a>\"语言编写的，由加纳的一名软件工程师<a href=\"https://github.com/profclems?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">Clement Sam</a>\"于2020年7月创建，自那时起已有<a href=\"https://github.com/profclems/glab/graphs/contributors?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">80多名贡献者</a>\"参与开发。其目标是提供与<a href=\"https://github.com/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">GitHub</a>\" CLI工具<a href=\"https://cli.github.com/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">gh</a>\"类似的功能，包括处理<a href=\"https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/user/project/issues/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">GitLab Issue</a>\"和合并请求，以及观察直接从CLI运行的管道。glab可用于<a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">SaaS产品</a>\"和<a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/install/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">自托管GitLab</a>\"。GitLab CLI使用glab <command />  [flags]这样的结构来执行之前只能从GitLab用户界面执行的<a href=\"https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/integration/glab/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">许多任务</a>\"。</p><p></p><p>GitLab的<a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/direction/create/editor_extension/#where-we-are-headed?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">目标</a>\"是让开发人员把更多的精力放在有意义的工作上，让他们可以使用流行的带有<a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=gitlab.gitlab-workflow&amp;accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">GitLab工作流插件</a>\"的编辑器<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">VS Code</a>\"。随着GitLab与CLI的集成并被正式采用，开发人员不再需要频繁地在Web浏览器和终端之间切换。之前，开发人员需要使用<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">git命令行</a>\"进行文件<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/docs/git-commit?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">提交</a>\"、<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/docs/git-push?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">推送</a>\"和<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/docs/git-pull?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">拉取</a>\"，然后在Web浏览器中创建相关的<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/36666408?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">合并请求</a>\"和运行<a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/blog/2019/07/12/guide-to-ci-cd-pipelines/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">管道</a>\"。</p><p></p><p>随着过去几个月采用量的增长，GitLab在更大范围内提升了glab的安全性，因为GitLab的应用程序安全团队已经对这个工具进行了评审，确保它对用户是安全的。glab使用GitLab的<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Personal_access_token?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">个人访问令牌</a>\"（PAT）进行身份验证，与其他管理代码的CLI和GUI工具类似。</p><p></p><p>现在，这个工具的<a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/cli/-/releases/v1.24.1?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">1.24.1版本已经发布</a>\"，并重新命名为GitLab CLI，由GitLab自己托管。开发社区在经过这个过渡之后也保留了下来——自被采用以来的来自社区的近40项贡献，包括创建者Clement本人的。未来的版本有望解决项目中积压的一些问题，GitLab已经表示愿意了解社区想从这个CLI工具中得到什么，以及如何增强它，以进一步改进开发者的工作流程。</p><p></p><p>glab CLI现在可以从GitLab上的<a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/cli/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">代码库</a>\"中获得，并且可以安装在macOS、Windows和Linux上。</p><p></p><p>原文链接：</p><p><a href=\"https://www.infoq.com/news/2022/12/gitlab-adopts-glab-cli/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzI5ODE2OTMsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiUXZMYnZIZnEwbTBteVFuTiIsImlhdCI6MTY3Mjk4MTM5MywiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.7I38f2qXVP0n5LaO6ZHZ5hThxqOXSpKotPMuS6T5s6k\">https://www.infoq.com/news/2022/12/gitlab-adopts-glab-cli/</a>\"</p><p></p><p>相关阅读：</p><p><a href=\"https://www.infoq.cn/article/WVFywuP2fdbCFh43k3QT\">GitLab发布单租户SaaS产品，实现严格的安全性和合规性</a>\"</p><p><a href=\"https://xie.infoq.cn/article/77e35ab64dd13dd314dede926\">如何利用极狐 GitLab CI/CD 完成 Jenkins 的迁移</a>\"</p>",
